e,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n12380"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to insert"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fill in; to wrap up, to envelop, to swathe"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fill in; to list, to record, to incorporate, to introduce"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"See the etymology of the corresponding lemma form."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n12380","headword_ar":"ادرج","root":"drj","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(God)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused"},{"kind":"text","text":"people"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to pass away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perish."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [See also 10.]) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Adrjhu","text_ar":"ادرجهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAls~ayofi","text_ar":"بِالسَّيْفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He destroyed him with the sword"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$mr","text_ar":"شمر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tudoziju garoDahaA watuloHiquhu biHaqabihaA","text_ar":"تُدْزِجُ غَرْضَهَا وَتُلْحِقُهُ بِحَقَبِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a she-camel when she makes her saddle with its appertenances to shift backwards ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She makes her fore girth to slip back and to become close to her kind girth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) Accord. to Aboo-Tálib,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idoraAjN","text_ar":"اـِدْرَاجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies A camel's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"becoming lank in the belly, so that his belly-girth shifts back to the kind girth; the load also shifting back."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Adrj Ald~alowa","text_ar":"ادرج الدَّلْوَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drew up the bucket gently:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drew it up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out, by little and little."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Riyáshee, TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Adrj AlA_iqaAmapa","text_ar":"ادرج الاـِقَامَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajahaA","text_ar":"دَرَجَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darojN","text_ar":"دَرْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arosalahaA","text_ar":"اَرْسَلَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He chanted the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iqaAmap","text_ar":"اـِقَامَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.); meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he chanted it in a quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an uninterrupted, manner;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for such is the usual"},{"kind":"page_break","n":868},{"kind":"text","text":"and prescribed manner of doing so: see 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H*m","text_ar":"حذم"},{"kind":"text","text":": in the present day,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daraja","text_ar":"دَرَجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. and inf. n. as above, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he chanted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sang, in a trilling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quavering, manner;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uninterruptedly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) ―         -b5-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idoraAjN","text_ar":"اـِدْرَاجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in speaking signifies, in like manner, The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conjoining of words, without pausing; i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waSolN","text_ar":"وَصْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqofN","text_ar":"وَقْفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": it occurs in this sense in the S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hl","text_ar":"هل"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.] ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Adrj","text_ar":"ادرج"},{"kind":"text","text":"(inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idoraAjN","text_ar":"اـِدْرَاجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA) also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He folded, folded up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rolled up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K,) a thing, (TA,) a writing, (S, A, Msb,) and a garment, or piece of cloth; (Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dr~j","text_ar":"درّج","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tadoriyjN","text_ar":"تَدْرِيجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daraja","text_ar":"دَرَجَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darojN","text_ar":"دَرْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the first of these verbs is the most chaste: (L:) [it signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he rolled"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like a scroll; made"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into a roll,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scroll:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"round like a scroll; he rounded"},{"kind":"text","text":"it: (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adomaja","text_ar":"اَدْمَجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mudomajN","text_ar":"مُدْمَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mudamolajN","text_ar":"مُدَمْلَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Har~ada","text_ar":"حَرَّدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he wound"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing upon another thing:] also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he infolded"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inserted"},{"kind":"text","text":"it: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he wrapped, wrapped up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inwrapped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing in another thing. (L.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adoraja AlkitaAba fiY AlkitaAbi","text_ar":"اَدْرَجَ الكِتَابَ فِى الكِتَابِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He infolded, enclosed, or inserted, the writing in the"},{"kind":"text","text":"[other]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"writing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put it within it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Adrj","text_ar":"ادرج"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almay~ita fiY Alkafani waAlqabori","text_ar":"المَيِّتَ فِى الكَفَنِ وَالقَبْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put the dead man into the grave-clothing and the grave."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adorajaniY fiY TaY~ Aln~isoyaAni","text_ar":"اَدْرَجَنِى فِى طَىّ النِّسْيَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, infolded me in the folding of oblivion"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TwY","text_ar":"طوى"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b7-  [And hence, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He foisted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inserted spuriously,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a verse or verses into a poem.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajaEa","text_ar":"رَجَعَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idoraAjahu","text_ar":"اـِدْرَاجَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY A_idoraAjihi","text_ar":"عَلَى اـِدْرَاجِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darajN","text_ar":"دَرَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adorajato","text_ar":"اَدْرَجَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a she-camel: see 1.       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Adrj biAln~aAqapi","text_ar":"ادرج بِالنَّاقَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bound"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sar~a","text_ar":"صَرَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the she-camel's teats"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"durojap","text_ar":"دُرْجَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of rag wrapped about them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["God","K","S","A","Msb","TA","L"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}